Geta. Yes, but do you know how deeply? Listen to what happened. Next day he went straight to the old woman, and implored her to let him have the girl. She refused, and said that what he asked was not right3 that the girl was a citizen of Athens, a good girl of a good family. If he wanted her for his wife, she would agree to his marrying her legally3 if not, she would have nothing to do with him.
